<p style="Normal" xid="622" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">Neurocognitive Linguistics Laboratory<br/>User Manual<pbr/><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="626" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr"><c></c>Revision History</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">Gordon Tisher &lt;gordon@balafon.net&gt;<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="3" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">v1.1.0, October 2010: Rewritten from old Wiki version.<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="620" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">v1.2.0, March 2011: Added section on Grids.</p>
